A memorial service of the late Ngina Rose happened on Monday at Consolata Shrine in Westlands, Nairobi. The service was attended by friends and family of the late, among the President Uhuru Kenyatta and wife Margaret Kenyatta. The late Ngina leaves behind her husband Manga Mugwe, children Njeri and Kevin, Nyakio and Jerry, Mugwe and Natalie and Ciani,Â and her grandchildren Heri, Anya, Khajia and Ngina.